title: Boulding on Rise in Business School Applications
itunes:title: Boulding on Rise in Business School Applications
description:
William Boulding, Dean of The Fuqua School of Business at Duke University, discusses business schools seeing a rise in applications despite the bad economy.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Kailey Leinz. Producer: Doni Holloway.
